N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 95.10 - Stenographic record

State Regulations
A stenographic record shall be made by the hearing. Upon request, a transcript will be made available for examination. Copies may be procured upon payment of the charge therefor. Notes
